    public interface PsiTypeParameter
extends PsiClass, PsiAnnotationOwner, JvmTypeParameter
    Represents the type parameter of a generic class, interface, method or constructor.

        default boolean hasAnnotation(java.lang.String fqn)
        Description copied from interface: PsiAnnotationOwner
        Searches the owner for an annotation with the specified fully qualified name and returns true if it is found.

        This method is preferable over PsiAnnotationOwner.findAnnotation(java.lang.String) since implementations are free not to instantiate the PsiAnnotation.
